│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ **3. Implementation**                                                                                                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ I will use `sed` to insert `if (isa<Instruction>(Op0) && isa<Instruction>(Op1))` before the existing `if` statement. The line number from the stack trace is a good guide.               │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
